snippet: At least one person was stabbed at Webster Hall and another was bitten, forcing promoters to cancel a show that was part of the CBGB Music Festival.
abstract: Stabbing at a concert at Webster Hall in Manhattan's East Village forces the club to shut down for the evening; show was part of the CBGB Music Festival featuring hardcore metal bands.
lead_paragraph: At least one person was stabbed at Webster Hall and another was bitten, forcing promoters to cancel a show that was part of the CBGB Music Festival.
